casebody.data:
Robert W. BRIGGS and Alyssa Lenhoff-Briggs, Plaintiffs-Appellees,
v.
Theodore SZYDLOWSKI and Nora Szydlowski, Defendants/Third-Party Plaintiffs,
and
Kidd & Leavy Real Estate Co., LLC, Defendant-Appellant,
and
Michael McCarthy and Rolling Meadows Properties, LLC, d/b/a Gaslight Group Properties, Third-Party Defendants. SC: 158650
COA: 340713 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 28, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the September 25, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
